{"tid":118074,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"床 邊 毛 公 仔 的 五 大 好 用 處","createTime":"2017-02-12T17:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T20:23:38.000Z","uid":5077,"like":178,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30a0ff75006e39f7766037fb453e6e3c13259d89","tid":118074,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"一、當你夜晚感到寂寞的時候，可以跟他們聊聊天，細說一下今天所發生的事。<br />\n<br />\n二、寒冷夜剛躲進被竇的時候，身體還會覺得冷。此時只需要將毛公仔夾到兩邊腋下和大腿內側，就能讓你迅速感到溫暖。<br />\n<br />\n三、夜深時份，覺得肚空空又不想下床？撕開你的毛公仔吃內裡的綿花吧。綿花吞到胃部時會發脹，令你產生飽肚感。<br />\n<br />\n四、當你的伴侶不在身旁，想他想得難耐不堪的時候，就拿起你床邊的毛公仔，慢慢塞進下體磨擦吧。軟綿綿的體感就好似伴侶一直在身旁陪伴著你一樣。<br />\n<br />\n五、有朋友到訪，想要跟你同床睡覺談心事？好極，但當她談到一些令你不悅的事情時，你可嘗試用毛巾公掩住她的口鼻，直到她知錯，向你道歉為止。"},{"pid":"364d44f7b213ded25a2239cf2f0dfe021dd8f80c","tid":118074,"uid":16085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:26:08.000Z","msg":"唔怕夜晚瞓著之後啲毛公仔過嚟打鳩你？"},{"pid":"a81fde214ecbdf1f08409eef706ae705e85e5675","tid":118074,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:27:07.000Z","msg":"345<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307b61aeb4f0945be1250b345e83190d200fb02e","tid":118074,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"Btw 5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想俾女女塞口"},{"pid":"5e2596cab0b0bd80d328d523af69a4253243d93d","tid":118074,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>345<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過包你返唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"edf0c53362ea6ae241fca1c4200749147af355b2","tid":118074,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:41:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw 5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想俾女女塞口</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78