到訪，想要跟你同床睡覺談心事？好極，但當她談到一些令你不悅的事情時，你可嘗試用<span style=\"color: red;\">毛巾公</span>掩住她的口鼻，直到她知錯，向你道歉為止。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a940d7a8ca14b389da85b6166530384dab3e7035","tid":118074,"uid":35027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"五、有朋友到訪，想要跟你同床睡覺談心事？好極，但當她談到一些令你不悅的事情時，你可嘗試用<span style=\"color: red;\">毛巾公</span>掩住她的口鼻，直到她知錯，向你道歉為止"},{"pid":"8e53328a249a675e5f031b65ee03baa1fff0fcf2","tid":118074,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f9057c788d1ad4b0776c77d70531ed8199cfa9","tid":118074,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:43:59.000Z","msg":"諗起會然羊咩123b隻核突羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會都係咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90148d94a85a96f00d58fcd096740f4f27e657b3","tid":118074,"uid":54425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">仆你們街</span><br />\n打字都有鄉音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自細老母公公成日買公仔俾我<br />\n搞到我見到得意嘅公仔都會想要<br />\n依家床邊都有6隻腦魔陪住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打又邊到鄉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n345<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 